@startuml 04-modulith-modules
title HexaStock — Spring Modulith Application Modules

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ArrowColor #1f4e79
skinparam ComponentBorderColor #1f4e79
skinparam ComponentBackgroundColor #fff3cd
skinparam ComponentBackgroundColor<<leaf>> #d4edda

component "marketdata" <<leaf>> as marketdata
component "portfolios" as portfolios
component "watchlists" as watchlists
component "notifications" as notifications

portfolios     --> marketdata : allowedDependencies\n= {marketdata::model,\n   marketdata::port-out}
watchlists     --> marketdata : allowedDependencies\n= {marketdata::model}
notifications  --> watchlists : allowedDependencies\n= {watchlists, marketdata::model}\n(consumes domain event)
notifications  ..> marketdata : Ticker VO inside event payload

note bottom of marketdata
  Leaf module. No outgoing
  cross-module dependencies.
end note

note right of notifications
  Only module that knows about
  channels (Telegram, logging, ...).
  Subscribes to WatchlistAlertTriggeredEvent
  via @ApplicationModuleListener.
end note

note left of portfolios
  Owns Portfolio aggregate,
  FIFO trading orchestration,
  Transaction ledger.
  Does NOT depend on watchlists
  or notifications.
end note

@enduml
